BBC Global Questions - Trump's America: A Nation Divided 720p HDTV x264-MVGroup

One year on since Donald Trump's election to the most powerful position in the world, Global Questions travels to Charleston, South Carolina, to hear from people in the south. Zeinab Badawi, together with a high profile panel of political and public figures from South Carolina and beyond, find out what they think of his presidency and where America stands today
